name: Jamie´s Rebound
description:
Just an abandoned project that i recently found. I was modding Boxel Rebound cuz i liked that game. Its not finished (yet). But i already replaced sounds, music, buttons, and some levels

WARNINGS: Only levels 1-9 are changed. Also the game is hacked so you cant die of spikes and you can do multiple jumps. Game crashes when selecting level 40
